  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to sdl2-ttf</title>

    <para>
      <application>sdl2-ttf</application> is a wrapper around the FreeType and Harfbuzz libraries, allowing you to use TrueType fonts to render text in SDL applications.
    </para>

